---
title: Bacon, Mushroom & Leek Fettuccine with Chilli & Garlic Pangrattato
description: It's that time of the week again, pasta night and we’re here to twist things around. Herbs and mushrooms are a must in any
pasta dish, add leek and bacon, then garnish with a pangrattato for something a bit different and definitely delicious.
